Class RendererEditor

All Implemented Interfaces:
PropertyEditor
public class RendererEditor
extends PropertyEditorSupport

The RendererEditor class is used in the design-time bound with renderer property of a Layer bean in an IDE tool. It will create a CustomRendererEditor class which allows user set a simple renderer for a layer (in a string format) during the design-time.
